comments.comment: <denchmark-link:https://github.com/furkancoskun>@furkancoskun</denchmark-link> , could you please give us labels for your task (which you specified when you created the task) and a json file with annotations?
Also I tried the version with no segmentation, this consist of just bounding boxes, no segmentation. I tried with "segmentation": [ ]" but error was same.

<denchmark-link:https://github.com/furkancoskun>@furkancoskun</denchmark-link> Hi The cause of your problem is mismatch of the category_id field in the annotation section [0, 1] and the id field in categories section [1, 2].
<denchmark-link:https://github.com/furkancoskun>@furkancoskun</denchmark-link> , it seems the problem was resolved. Could you please confirm?
<denchmark-link:https://github.com/furkancoskun>@furkancoskun</denchmark-link> , I will close the issue. Please don't hesitate to open it again if you still have it.
